  "original_title": "\u0db4\u0dbd\u0dcf\u0dc0\u0dd2\u0dba \u0dbd\u0dd4\u0dab\u0dd4 \u0dc3\u0db8\u0dcf\u0d9c\u0db8\u0dda \u0dc3\u0dd2\u0dbb \u0d9a\u0dbb \u0dc3\u0dd2\u0da7\u0dd2 \u0db4\u0dd2\u0dbb\u0dd2\u0dc3 \u0db4\u0ddc\u0dbd\u0dd2\u0dc3\u0dca \u0db8\u0dd0\u0daf\u0dd2\u0dc4\u0dad\u0dca\u0dc0\u0dd3\u0db8\u0dd9\u0db1\u0dca \u0d91\u0dc5\u0dd2\u0dba\u0da7",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Police release group detained at Palaviya Salt Company",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Puttalam - The Palaviya Salt Company has released four (04) members of the board of directors, including the accountant, who were detained by the employees demanding an increase in their salaries, Puttalam Police said this morning (26).",
        "Puttalam - Employees of the Palaviya Salt Company have been on strike for several days demanding an increase of Rs. 10,000.",
        "Workers who have been on strike for the past 30 days, officials at the Puttalam Labor Office held a discussion with the board on the 23rd.",
        "It is reported that a sum of Rs. 5000.00 has been paid for a portion of the salary increase.",
        "The board of directors of the salt company had agreed to resolve the issue by the 27th, but the problem was exacerbated when the salt company's superintendent told its employees on the evening of the 25th that the company would have to close down as it was in a loss-making position.",
        "Police say that the employees who were alarmed by this statement have closed the main gate of the salt company and locked the four (04) members of the board including the accountant and the employees inside the company in groups and have taken action to guard the main gate.",
        "According to a complaint lodged with the Puttalam Police by the Superintendent of the Salt Company, a special police team had entered the back of the Salt Company this morning (26) and released the four (04) members of the Board including the Accountant who had been detained and taken to the Puttalam Police and sent home. ."
      ],
